{"tid":2120530,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"排球少年我好滾動呀！！！","createTime":"2020-07-22T17:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T10:57:04.000Z","uid":352932,"like":60,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"be26d4b5ab90d22ca6b1391ce85d4f3b370d379b","tid":2120530,"uid":352932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T17:55:30.000Z","msg":"小弟自己都係打排球 睇住翔陽由一個廢柴到打國家隊個種辛路歷程 真係唔係帶刺偉 龍馬 達也呢d角色可以相比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係我心目中佢係可以比得上Slam dunk<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當然大家可能話無咁epic 無咁熱血 無咁大迴響 <br />\n但我好想多謝古館老師為排球界畫左呢個代表作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陪伴住我人生同排球既成長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S. 試過同fd試怪人快攻 好7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b32eff5def5acd698a99e85c8e97c3c37927abd","tid":2120530,"uid":35105,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T17:58:04.000Z","msg":"神作不解釋"},{"pid":"6e6b47c717a450130c4ce3c35cad4226c2d28963","tid":2120530,"uid":213819,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T18:01:10.000Z","msg":"宜家難得一見既神作"},{"pid":"b7dece8935dcef611399014055315ae07e1ca104","tid":2120530,"uid":162539,"like":2,"dislike":33,"score":-31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T18:02:54.000Z","msg":"後期比賽啲技倆不停重覆，有啲悶"},{"pid":"530a077940e3700dfcf8aa695598467a854bcacc","tid":2120530,"uid":99745,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T18:04:08.000Z","msg":"套藍球少年都係差唔多套路"},{"pid":"7e8078161a58af23b7955c92ad4a0e77559bdfa2","tid":2120530,"uid":235778,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T18:05:47.000Z","msg":"寫實啲點都熱血過出技打波嘅"},{"pid":"4546760686a75022dce887f37413020612d87d68","tid":2120530,"uid":123895,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T21:34:56.000Z","msg":"冇咁epic我覺得係因為以前slam dunk年代冇咁多娛樂<br />\n如果排球以前出版分分鐘紅到仆街做埋一代經典<img s